Social Photos v2

This is a clone of the Social Photos Project that is live at http://socialphotos.net. Feel free to send PRs to add features/fix bugs/etc and i'll be more than happy to take a look. Please go through the file "TODO" to see a list of unimplemented ideas that can be implemented.

Link to list of reported issues: https://code.google.com/p/social-photos/issues/list

Feel free to fork and use it as you please. I'd appreciate a link back but it's not mandatory.


NOTE:
  
All the code in this project is under Creative Commons Public Domain License: http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

Anyone who is submitting Pull Requests to be merged into this project should be willing to publish their code under the same license too.
